OL,3,C'Mummy is not coming home': Family say
OL,4,Cwoman with post-natal depression
OL,5,C'failed'
OL,7,FLucy Pearson was under the care of
OL,8,FCross Lane Hospital, in Scarborough,
OL,9,Fwhen she was found dead after going
OL,10,Fmissing from the site in September
OL,11,Fthis year. Her family say she took her
OL,12,Fown life.
OL,14,FThe 37-year-old had been getting
OL,15,Ftreatment for post-natal depression
OL,16,Fwhich she had suffered with following
OL,17,Fthe birth of her son in October 2023.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/16
