OL,3,C'Mummy is not coming home': Family say
OL,4,Cwoman with post-natal depression
OL,5,C'failed'
OL,7,FShe had also suffered with the illness
OL,8,Fafter the birth of her daughter in
OL,9,F2021 and her family said they could
OL,10,Fnot understand why she was not given
OL,11,Fmore support throughout her second
OL,12,Fpregnancy, and in the months following
OL,13,Fher son's birth.
OL,15,FThey told ITV News that it was only
OL,16,Fwhen Lucy tried to take her own life
OL,17,Fthat was she referred to a perinatal
OL,18,Fcommunity mental health team, run by
OL,19,Fthe region's biggest mental health
OL,20,Fprovider, the Tees Esk and Wear
OL,21,FValleys NHS Foundation Trust.
