OL,3,C'Mummy is not coming home': Family say
OL,4,Cwoman with post-natal depression
OL,5,C'failed'
OL,7,FLucy's mother Ann Mullholland said it
OL,8,Fhelped at first but when face to face
OL,9,Fvisits were replaced by phone calls,
OL,10,Fher daughter's mental health
OL,11,Fdeteriorated further.
OL,13,FAnn said: "Lucy had a phone call and
OL,14,Fshe came off and she said 'well, she
OL,15,Fwas just ticking the boxes and she
OL,16,Fdidn't know anything about me. She
OL,17,Fobviously hadn't read my file'.
