OL,3,C'Mummy is not coming home': Family say
OL,4,Cwoman with post-natal depression
OL,5,C'failed'
OL,7,F"She said 'I feel let down'. Lucy's
OL,8,Fmental health deteriorated. We tried
OL,9,Fto integrate her into family life with
OL,10,Fher husband and children but she just
OL,11,Ffelt so sad when she saw other mums
OL,12,Flooking happy enjoying family time.
OL,14,F"She was so sad that she didn't feel
OL,15,Fgood enough to be a mum. She was so
OL,16,Fdesperate to end the pain in her
OL,17,Fheart."
