OL,3,C'Mummy is not coming home': Family say
OL,4,Cwoman with post-natal depression
OL,5,C'failed'
OL,7,FLucy's sister, Faye Wheldon, told ITV
OL,8,FNews that after a second suicide
OL,9,Fattempt, Lucy was admitted to Cross
OL,10,FLane mental health hospital in
OL,11,FScarborough as a voluntary patient.
OL,13,FBut she claimed "she was allowed to
OL,14,Fcome and go as she pleased". She also
OL,15,Fsaid staff underestimated her risk and
OL,16,Fthe family believed she should have
OL,17,Fbeen sectioned.
OL,19,FFaye said: "She was just vacant,
OL,20,Fdepressed, (the) absolute opposite of
OL,21,FLucy, and it was scary.
