OL,3,C'Mummy is not coming home': Family say
OL,4,Cwoman with post-natal depression
OL,5,C'failed'
OL,7,F"It was our absolutely last thing we
OL,8,Fwanted for my sister to go into a
OL,9,Fpsychiatric hospital. It was the last
OL,10,Fresort but we trusted them as the
OL,11,Fexperts and professionals to keep her
OL,12,Fsafe. But they did the complete
OL,13,Fopposite."
OL,15,FOn 23 September, Lucy's family said
OL,16,Fshe had been picked up from the
OL,17,Fhospital and signed out of her ward by
OL,18,Fher mother Ann who was taking her out
OL,19,Ffor lunch.
