OL,3,C'Mummy is not coming home': Family say
OL,4,Cwoman with post-natal depression
OL,5,C'failed'
OL,7,FThey told ITV News her mum dropped her
OL,8,Fback off outside the hospital
OL,9,Fentrance, but when they called her
OL,10,Fward to check on Lucy, they were told
OL,11,Fshe had not returned.
OL,13,FPolice found Lucy's body several miles
OL,14,Faway from the hospital that evening.
OL,16,FFaye described finding Lucy's body as
OL,17,Fa "living nightmare", adding that her
OL,18,Fdeath had ruined their lives.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/16
