OL,3,C'Mummy is not coming home': Family say
OL,4,Cwoman with post-natal depression
OL,5,C'failed'
OL,7,F"We knew Lucy the best, her family
OL,8,Fknew her best," she added. "When we
OL,9,Ftold them she was having dark
OL,10,Fthoughts, we wanted them to act on it.
OL,11,FThey didn't. They didn't keep her safe
OL,12,Fand I can't forgive that.
OL,14,F"Her little boy is only one and her
OL,15,Fdaughter is three. She is missing her,
OL,16,Fwe all are. Her daughter asks 'when is
OL,17,Fmummy coming home?' And it's like a
OL,18,Fphysical pain in my heart.
