OL,3,C'Mummy is not coming home': Family say
OL,4,Cwoman with post-natal depression
OL,5,C'failed'
OL,7,F"I will tell them Mummy was an
OL,8,Fincredible person and she loved them
OL,9,Fvery much and she didn't want them to
OL,10,Fleave. She wanted to be with them
OL,11,Fforever but sadly the illness took
OL,12,Fthat away."
OL,14,FThe Tees Esk and Wear Valleys NHS
OL,15,FFoundation Trust, which runs Cross
OL,16,FLane Hospital, has been repeatedly
OL,17,Fcriticised over recent years by
OL,18,Ffamilies who have lost loved one under
OL,19,Fits care.
