OL,3,C'Mummy is not coming home': Family say
OL,4,Cwoman with post-natal depression
OL,5,C'failed'
OL,7,FIt is rated as 'requires improvement'
OL,8,Fby the Care Quality Commission.
OL,10,FIn its last inspection report,
OL,11,Fpublished in October 2023, concerns
OL,12,Fwere raised around safety, leadership
OL,13,Fand how the trust responds to patient
OL,14,Fneeds.
OL,16,FThe report did say, however, that
OL,17,Fthere had been "positive changes" in
OL,18,Fits senior leadership and there was
OL,19,Fnow a more open and transparent
OL,20,Fculture. The trust no longer had any
OL,21,Fservices rated as inadequate.
