OL,7,FResponding to the concerns raised by
OL,8,FLucy's family following her death a
OL,9,Ftrust spokesperson said: "Our hearts
OL,10,Fgo out to Lucy's family and friends.
OL,12,F"We are looking closely at the care
OL,13,FLucy received from us and, in keeping
OL,14,Fwith national guidance, we will
OL,15,Festablish if there is anything
OL,16,Fdifferent we could have done to
OL,17,Fprevent Lucy's death.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUtD@AOU
