OL,7,F"We will support Lucy's family through
OL,8,Fthis process as their involvement is
OL,9,Fincredibly important. Until that is
OL,10,Fcomplete, and an inquest has taken
OL,11,Fplace, we're unable to share further
OL,12,Fdetails with the media."
OL,14,FLucy's family also believe there
OL,15,Fshould have been more support in the
OL,16,Fprimary care setting, including with
OL,17,Fher GP.
